04:37.614 --> 04:41.334
- Hm!
- I win.

04:41.368 --> 04:43.870
W-what?!
That was a good move.

04:43.954 --> 04:46.789
- Thanks.
- Dogcopter, how do you do it?

04:46.874 --> 04:50.593
- How do I do what?
- I mean, what's your secret?

04:50.677 --> 04:53.713
- How'd you get so talented?
- Don't focus so much on

04:53.797 --> 04:57.425
talent, Steven. Making art
is all about communication.

04:57.426 --> 05:01.053
A piece of art is a conversation.
Every choice you make

05:01.104 --> 05:03.890
is a statement.

05:03.941 --> 05:06.859
Don't worry about labels
or conforming to a standard.

05:06.894 --> 05:09.979
Just be true to yourself and
people will appreciate

05:10.063 --> 05:11.781
your honesty.
Ahh.

05:11.865 --> 05:14.700
Whoa...
Thanks for the advice.

05:14.735 --> 05:18.821
- And take a deep breath.
- What?

05:22.159 --> 05:26.546
<i>Here again?
I don't know what this place is</i>

05:26.580 --> 05:31.834
<i>but it feels...familiar.
Why can't I breathe?</i>

05:31.919 --> 05:34.921
<i>Wait a minute... Lion!</i>

05:38.809 --> 05:42.929
Lion, my face is not your bed!
What's going on with you?

05:43.842 --> 05:45.498
You just wanted a belly rub?

05:46.099 --> 05:49.435
You never let me touch
your belly! Oh!

05:50.813 --> 05:52.104
It's a trap!

05:53.532 --> 05:54.824
An adorable trap!

05:56.301 --> 05:57.693
Okay you got me!

05:57.778 --> 06:01.281
Will you let me go?

06:01.615 --> 06:03.445
Come on now!

06:04.701 --> 06:06.786
That's it!

06:06.837 --> 06:11.123
Let's go lion, you're on a time out!

06:11.208 --> 06:15.595
I said, you're on time out!
You're gonna stay out here

06:15.629 --> 06:19.687
and think about what you did!

06:31.228 --> 06:34.113
He loves me!

06:34.147 --> 06:36.532
Aww, I just can't stay mad at you!

06:36.617 --> 06:38.901
You're a wonderful pink human being.

06:38.986 --> 06:42.905
Except you're not.
'Cause you're a lion.

06:59.006 --> 07:02.058
<i>I'm inside lion's mane?!</i>

07:14.134 --> 07:18.190
Sorry, I couldn't resist.

07:18.275 --> 07:21.777
<i>Am I...
supposed to do something here?</i>

07:21.862 --> 07:23.446
<i>Wha ...?</i>

07:30.037 --> 07:32.838
<i>Mm... </i>

07:52.225 --> 07:54.777
<i>For me?
Who would put this here?</i>

07:54.895 --> 07:58.064
<i>And how does this huge place
fit inside of lion's mane anyw ...</i>

07:58.115 --> 08:01.450
<i>Mm...</i>

08:06.974 --> 08:10.418
...and he keeps
sleeping on Steven's face!

08:10.419 --> 08:13.127
But Steven doesn't want me
watching him anymore.

08:13.205 --> 08:15.881
<i>So one of you two has to do it.</i>

08:20.170 --> 08:22.972
- Sadie! Sadie!
- Steven, you know donuts

08:23.056 --> 08:26.092
aren't ready for another hour.

08:26.143 --> 08:28.575
Really? Come on!

08:49.183 --> 08:50.533
<i>What are you doing?</i>

08:50.617 --> 08:55.788
Steven, that voice.

08:55.839 --> 08:59.208
<i>Greg made a friend.</i>

08:59.292 --> 09:02.011
<i>What?! Ah!</i>

09:06.967 --> 09:09.301
<i>- Go on...
- Sorry, I'm getting stage</i>

09:09.352 --> 09:12.021
<i>- fright here.
- Tell us about yourself.</i>

09:12.105 --> 09:15.691
<i>Well, let's see here...
My name is Greg.</i>

09:15.776 --> 09:17.670
<i>No, no, no! This is all wrong!</i>

09:17.932 --> 09:20.062
<i>Okay, go!</i>

09:20.147 --> 09:22.815
<i>They call me...</i>

09:22.949 --> 09:26.619
<i>Mr. Universe! Get
ready baby, you're gonna</i>

09:26.653 --> 09:29.155
<i>have the coolest dad
this side of the cosmos!</i>

09:31.617 --> 09:33.993
<i>Press the button, Rose!</i>

09:34.077 --> 09:37.663
<i>Oh, right!
Was that the right one?</i>

09:37.748 --> 09:41.167
<i>- Uh... maybe?
- Oh, what does this one do?</i>

09:43.920 --> 09:46.547
<i>Isn't it remarkable, Steven?</i>

09:46.548 --> 09:49.877
<i>This world is full of
so many possibilities.</i>

09:49.878 --> 09:54.872
<i>Each living thing has an
entirely unique experience.</i>

09:54.873 --> 09:57.016
<i>The sights they see,
the sounds they hear.</i>

09:57.067 --> 10:01.187
<i> The lives they live are so</i>

10:01.271 --> 10:04.907
<i>complicated... a-and so simple.</i>

10:04.991 --> 10:08.054
<i>I can't wait for you to join them.</i>

10:08.857 --> 10:12.796
<i>Steven, we can't both exist.</i>

10:12.797 --> 10:16.735
<i>I'm going to become half of you.</i>

10:16.803 --> 10:20.005
<i>And I need you to know that
every moment you love being</i>

10:20.073 --> 10:25.077
<i>yourself, that's me, loving
you and loving being you.</i>

10:25.145 --> 10:30.015
<i>Because you're going to
be something extraordinary.</i>

10:30.050 --> 10:33.135
<i>You're going to be a human being.</i>

10:33.220 --> 10:37.223
<i>- Hey, Rose!
- Take care of them, Steven.</i>

10:48.118 --> 10:52.288
Hey, Sadie, come on we got to open up!

11:01.081 --> 11:03.415
What in the world did you guys watch?

11:09.089 --> 11:12.398
Hey, mom?
You know how I said you didn't

11:12.437 --> 11:14.158
have to make me those lunches anymore?

